Key Match Events: Brilliant partnership by Rahmanullah Gurbaz and Ibrahim Zadaran helped Afghanistan post 183/5 against Uganda
Fazalhaq Farooqi took five wickets while Naveen-Ul-Haq and Rashid Khan scalped two wickets each
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at the Providence Stadium in Guyana
Others: Uganda were reduced to 18 for 5 inside the first five overs
Rashid Khan was the captain of Afghanistan
